data.description: Welcome to this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a den and a refreshing pool, eagerly awaiting its new owners. You'll notice recent upgrades, including a new roof and laminate flooring in the bedrooms and den, all completed in 2023. Upon entering, you'll find a practical layout that makes daily living a breeze. To your right, you'll discover a functional kitchen, perfect for everyday cooking and family gatherings. Moving through the foyer, the living room awaits, with French doors leading to the enclosed lanai, where the pool invites you to relax. Adjacent to the living room is a versatile den, adaptable to your needs. The kitchen seamlessly connects to both the dining area and a cozy breakfast nook, ensuring effortless entertainment. The primary suite, conveniently located off the dining area, boasts two walk-in closets and an ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub, double vanity, and a walk-in shower. A split floor plan offers two additional bedrooms situated off the living room, sharing a bathroom and a linen closet for added storage. The lanai provides an ideal spot to unwind, featuring a covered area for shade and a pool for those sunny Florida days. The backyard offers ample room for you to personalize the outdoor space to your liking. Additionally, there are three wells, ensuring a reliable water source, and the septic tank was recently serviced in 2023. Nestled in the thriving community of North Port, you'll have access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options, including Atwater Community Park and the North Port Aquatic Center. Embrace the Florida lifestyle and make this inviting property your new home today.
